[{"id":"FT553926","type":"longtextV2","stimulusHtml":"<p><strong>Directions:</strong> Suggested planning and writing time—35 minutes.</p>\n\n<p>Write an essay that:</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>Has a relevant thesis.</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>Addresses all parts of the question.</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>Supports thesis with specific evidence.</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>Is well organized.</p>\n\t</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Analyze the ways in which the two works above, Perugino’s <em>Christ Delivering the Keys of the Kingdom to Saint Peter</em> (1481–1483) on the left, and Michelangelo’s <em>David</em> (1501–1504) on the right, represent the values of Italian Renaissance culture.</p>\n","features":[{"type":"sharedpassage","html":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"An engraving shows Perugino’s Christ delivering the keys of the Kingdom to Saint Peter. It shows the Christ handing a key to the kneeling Saint Peter, while the apostles stand in groups behind them. It also shows certain figures around them in contemporary dresses, who seem to witness the momentous event. In the center of the painting is the porticoes Temple of Solomon, with triumphal arches on its either side. It shows bluish-gray hills at a distance on either side of the temple, with feathery trees against the cloud-filled sky.\" height=\"382\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/537/media.academicmerit.com/6037766f7612e7dae09cd02fb210bc21/original.png\" width=\"600\" /></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"A monochrome shows the statue of Michelangelo’s David. It is a marble statue of a nude male carrying a slingshot over his shoulder and standing over the slain Goliath. It shows David standing relaxed, but alert. The figure stands with one leg holding its full weight and the other leg forward, causing the figure’s hips and shoulders to rest at opposite angles, giving a slight s-curve to the entire torso.\" height=\"543\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/537/media.academicmerit.com/de8e1aad7cda7289f3b44fc4ad37fd92/original.png\" width=\"300\" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n"}]}]